extras.optText:
##### State Machine Example How-To 

This template uses *Dialog* and *Function* nodes to simulate a basic Finite State
Machine example. It is inspired by a vending machine, where you can put some
coins in and get some items out.

Follow these steps to test this template;

**1.** Edit the Config Node

**2.** Set the msg.coin field to the amount of extra coins you want to get at 
the beginning. (Optional)
